"""Bundled Chinese name tables. Generated -- do not edit by hand.

Merged from the two hand-maintained tables that had drifted apart in
Stock_LineBot (`TW/US/CN_STOCK_MAPPING`) and Discord_StockBot
(`TW_STOCK_NAMES`, `STOCK_NAME_MAP`). The merge found no conflicting entries:
the tables agreed wherever they overlapped, they simply covered different
symbols -- which is exactly why keeping two of them was pointless.

Coverage is common listings only. Use :func:`yolab_quote.names.register`
to add your own.
"""

from __future__ import annotations

